e":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e68fd5ba5ff00ad01c002a005a660895dfe9fde8","tid":1136661,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"咁寸?<br />\n一陣港共話要解散立法會，唔批錢比立法會就好笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"解散都冇用<br />\n法律顧問唔係議員黎<br />\n係屬於秘書處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"立法會咪又係政府出糧<br />\n再駁咀唔比錢，自己出去搵過份工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffe6b3242da1286b789357ea112805197440bde","tid":1136661,"uid":95138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"法律顧問亦關注，修例後立法會不會再審議移交逃犯的安排，要求政府澄清，政府如何按《基本法》第64條，向立法會負責。"},{"pid":"d732660f69302862bf3699c46ac29a6a7ae2d7a7","tid":1136661,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99998303d548df593d1727ed97065ad4e395bc19","tid":1136661,"uid":187961,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"應該係想縮沙，所以開始搵落台階"},{"pid":"2fc613ea630d2d7a20d0de0852aab82048100cab","tid":1136661,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"點解係顧問做呢啲<br />\n佢唔係只就立法會相關事務既legal野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87877b86173ddcc4d6d1d2b20e34019c9d8473b5","tid":1136661,"uid":180880,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"2fc613ea630d2d7a20d0de0852aab82048100cab","tid":1136661,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"點解係顧問做呢啲<br />\n佢唔係只就立法會相關事務既legal野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"叫得做法律顧問<br />\n要審視政府交俾立法會既條例草案<br />\n有模糊既地方要政府回覆、釐清同修改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3544e3ea370254a17b4608786a01707bce30d39","tid":1136661,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"456e23898224926de4bf9dfb63d584f16b05a62f","tid":1136661,"uid":237425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"141c1d21bc2afee2fa4ccf9f3f582323516f037a","tid":1136661,"uid":6497,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e68fd5ba5ff00ad01c002a005a660895dfe9fde8","tid":1136661,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"咁寸?<br />\n一陣港共話要解散立法會，唔批錢比立法會就好笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"解散都冇用<br />\n法律顧問唔係議員黎<br />\n係屬於秘書處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"立法會咪又係政府出糧<br />\n再駁咀唔比錢，自己出去搵過份工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"<strong>立法會秘書處 (法律事務部)</strong><br />\n法律事務部負責就法案及附屬法例擬備法律報告，並就與委員會議事程序有關的法律事宜，向立法會各個委員會提供意見。秘書處的法律顧問亦是立法機關的法律顧問，就與立法會議事程序有關的法律事宜，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">向立法會主席及立法會秘書提供意見</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n根據《基本法》第71條，立法會主席由議員互選產生。第六屆立法會主席的選舉於2016年10月12日，即新一屆立法會任期開始的首次會議上舉行，並<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">由梁君彥議員當選為第六屆立法會主席</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>梁君彥</strong></span></span>:修訂逃犯條例直上大會未必可取<br />\n<br />\n【逃犯條例】法案具爭議 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>梁君彥</strong></span></span>：引《議事規則》91條未必可取<br />\n<br />\n政府出糧咪又係立法會批，你問下梁君彥搞乜先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361dbab1497498b2e18333a264dcec598356ff20","tid":1136661,"uid":143241,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:27:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪三權分立囉"},{"pid":"7c90fd5ed663114100304ce9a5b6eb36e240b4f8","tid":1136661,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"開始反啦<br />\n花生價格暴漲"},{"pid":"855602962c00d85155e4798d1ba817e675b3ed2a","tid":1136661,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3862f763b3c54b83bb5d6a4af6d9ce114c443ab8","tid":1136661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"reasonable"},{"pid":"8f42fb375fdfc52c5de9f1adae9c92edc3f30445","tid":1136661,"uid":12015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T10:21:56.000Z","msg":"港府回應指，有關1997年的做法已不合時宜，為堵塞現時漏洞及深化落實一國兩制和基本法，有必要重新檢視有關條例，以配合社會實際需要，並保障市民利益。而有關指導原則將會在條例修訂後得以鞏固和全面落實。<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"cadb9bc1bd1b463108ee8fffd0f1974309418dfe","tid":1136661,"uid":136216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係想縮沙，所以開始搵落台階</blockquote><br />\n現在得班民建聯，工聯會和777不顧超過十三萬人上街強行立法逃犯條例，台灣陸委會今天已經講到明若以逃犯條例危害香港人外，還危害住在香港台灣人人生安全;透先Apple daily 報導，李柱銘和吳藹議已經決定前往美國加拿大，說明逃犯條例危險地方&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"e6dea0f55223f7fafdf2f8d37c44f4831015ee8d","tid":1136661,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T12:21:30.000Z","msg":"Well done<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}